  "majesticmoth": "Majestic Moth raises the user's highest calculated base stat by 1 stage when it enters battle.",
  "souleater": "When the user knocks out an opponent with a direct hit, it immediately recovers 25% of its maximum HP.",
  "soullinker": "When the user takes a direct hit, the opponent takes identical damage. When landing a direct hit, the user also takes the same damage it inflicts. Does not activate when either Pokemon is knocked out, taking damage from Pain Split, or against another Soul Linker.",
  "sweetdreams": "Sweet Dreams restores 1/8 of maximum HP at the end of each turn when the user is asleep or has the Comatose ability. Additionally, it grants immunity to Bad Dreams damage.",
  "badluck": "Foes can not land critical hits, always roll minimum damage (85% instead of 85-100%), fail to inflict secondary effects that are not guaranteed, and have a 5% chance to miss a move.",
  "hauntedspirit": "Curses the attacker when knocked out by a direct hit. The curse inflicts 25% max HP damage per turn until the cursed Pokemon switches out or faints. Ghost-type attackers are immune to the curse.",
  "electricburst": "Electric Burst boosts Electric- type moves by 35% but causes 10% recoil damage based on damage dealt (minimum 1 HP). The recoil damage will not knock out the user.",
