  "looter": "When the user knocks out an opponent with a direct hit, it immediately recovers 25% of its maximum HP.",
  "lunareclipse": "Lunar Eclipse grants STAB bonus to both Fairy and Dark-type moves regardless of the user's typing. Improves Hypnosis accuracy to 90%.",
