  "discipline": "After using any Electric-type move, Thundercall automatically triggers a follow-up Smite attack at 20% power (24 base power). This physical Electric attack has an 80% accuracy, can paralyze targets (20% chance), and applies the Smack Down effect - grounding Flying-types.",
