  "frostburn": "Triggers a 40 BP Ice Beam immediately after using any Fire-type move.",
  "itchydefense": "Itchy Defense traps attackers with Infestation when the user is successfully hit by a contact move. The trapped opponent loses 1/8th of their maximum HP damage each turn for 4-5 turns and cannot switch out.",
