  "dustcloud": "Uses Sand Attack on the opponent upon switching into battle, reducing the target's accuracy by one stage.",
  "berserkerrage": "When hit, raises the user's Special Attack by 1 stage or maximizes it on critical hits. When the user knocks out an opponent, it instantly recovers from recharge status, allowing immediate use of moves like Hyper Beam without waiting.",
