  "yukionna": "Lowers both Attack and Special Attack of opposing Pokemon upon entry by one stage. Additionally provides a 30% chance to infatuate (cuts their Attack and Special Attack in half) the target on contact. Works offensively and defensively. This only works on the opposite gender.",
