  "telekinetic": "Casts Telekinesis on entry. All moves against the target cannot miss, but they become immune to Ground-type moves and other Grounded effects. Cannot affect Rooted Pokemon or if they hold Iron Ball. Wears off under Gravity or if they are hit by Smack Down. Lasts 3 turns.",
