  "monstermash": "Casts Trick-or-Treat on entry, adding Ghost type to the target. They do not benefit from the effects of fog. The effect persists until the target switches out.",
  "twostep": "After using a dance move, automatically follows up with a 50 BP Revelation Dance. The follow-up move matches the user's primary type.",
  "spiteful": "Spiteful reduces the attacker's PP by 4 when hit by contact moves. Targets the last move used by the attacker. Fails if the attacker has no remaining PP or hasn't used any moves yet.",
