  "permanence": "Prevents all opposing Pokemon from healing through any means. Blocks healing moves like Recover, absorbing moves like Drain Punch, passive healing from Leftovers and abilities like Regenerator, and prevents health recovery from berries and other items.",
  "hubris": "Boosts the user's Special Attack by one stage whenever it knocks out an opponent with a direct hit.",
  "cosmicdaze": "Attacks against confused and enraged targets deal double damage. Additionally, confused and enraged enemies take twice as much damage when they hurt themselves from those statuses.",
  "mindseye": "Mind's Eye allows Normal and Fighting-type moves to hit Ghost-type Pokemon with normal effectiveness. Additionally, this ability prevents the user's accuracy stat from being lowered by opposing moves or abilities.",
  "bloodprice": "Blood Price boosts all attacking moves by 30%, but the user loses 10% of their max hp when landing an attack.",
  "spikearmor": "Spike Armor has a 30% chance to inflict bleeding on contact moves, both when attacking and being attacked. Bleeding causes 1/16 max HP damage per turn, prevents healing, and negates the effects of stat stages. Rock and Ghost types are immune to bleeding.",
