  "worldserpent": "Physical non-contact moves deal 20% more damage. Contact moves have a 50% chance to trap the target for 4-5 turns.",
  "luckywings": "Doubles the activation chance of the user's secondary effects on their attacks. Boosts the power of all wing, wind, and air-based moves by 30%.",
  "komodo": "Changes the user's Normal-type moves to Dragon-type. If the user is Dragon-type its Dragon-type moves deal neutral damage vs Fairy, otherwise it gains Dragon STAB. The user has a 30% chance to poison the target after landing any move. Multihits roll the activation chance on each hit.",
  "envenom": "The user has a 30% to poison the target after landing any move. Multihits roll the activation chance on each hit.",
